Oi, bocah yang di tengah.

131
00:09:49,900 --> 00:09:51,680
Beri ruang untuk Marie!

132
00:09:51,680 --> 00:09:53,170
Dengan begitu, dia bisa
sembuh lebih cepat.

133
00:09:53,170 --> 00:09:55,870
Duh, jangan begitu dong, Kakak!

134
00:09:55,870 --> 00:09:57,360
Kau memang terpuji, Marie.

135
00:09:57,360 --> 00:09:59,370
Kebaikanmu bagaikan malaikat.

136
00:09:59,370 --> 00:10:01,540
Dan malaikat lebih
pantas di tengah-tengah!

137
00:10:01,540 --> 00:10:04,410
Di mana pun dia berdiri,
efek sihirnya sama saja!

138
00:10:04,410 --> 00:10:07,240
Marie, mau makan kentang kering, tidak?

139
00:10:07,240 --> 00:10:08,490
Biar energimu pulih kembali!

140
00:10:08,490 --> 00:10:10,780
Mana mungkin Marie mau
makan makanan tak jelas itu!

141
00:10:10,780 --> 00:10:13,390
Oi, di desaku ini terkenal, lo!

142
00:10:14,350 --> 00:10:18,150
Asta, kau dibesarkan
di gereja di Hage, 'kan?

143
00:10:18,830 --> 00:10:20,470
Kenapa Nenek bisa tahu?

144
00:10:21,150 --> 00:10:25,730
Sister Lily pernah
berguru di gereja kami.

145
00:10:25,730 --> 00:10:28,690
Dan saat itu dia
bercerita soal dirimu.

146
00:10:28,690 --> 00:10:30,180
Astaga!

147
00:10:30,180 --> 00:10:32,170
Nenek kenal Sister Lily, ya?

148
00:10:32,170 --> 00:10:34,600
Dia wanita yang luar biasa.

149
00:10:34,600 --> 00:10:36,310
Pastinya!

150
00:10:36,310 --> 00:10:40,300
