menghilang entah ke mana.

327
00:20:27,160 --> 00:20:30,010
Lindungi anak-anak,
Gauche, Asta!

328
00:20:30,010 --> 00:20:31,020
Baik!

329
00:20:33,290 --> 00:20:34,250
Ayo, Marie.

330
00:20:34,250 --> 00:20:35,890
Kakak?

331
00:20:35,890 --> 00:20:36,910
Pergi?

332
00:20:37,010 --> 00:20:38,360
Tapi, bagaimana dengan yang lain?

333
00:20:38,360 --> 00:20:42,670
Aku tak peduli, terlalu berbahaya kalau
kau dekat-dekat dengan monster itu!

334
00:20:45,650 --> 00:20:46,690
Si bodoh itu...

335
00:20:53,740 --> 00:20:58,230
Kali ini aku pasti akan
membawamu pulang, Asta!

336
00:21:10,010 --> 00:21:11,370
Kakak.

337
00:22:43,810 --> 00:22:46,770
Semanggi Kerdil!

338
00:22:48,190 --> 00:22:50,180
Go! Go! Gordon!

339
00:22:51,300 --> 00:22:55,260
Aku sudah minta bantuan,
